  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="content">
    <h1>About The Cerf Report</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">More signal. Less noise.</p>
    
    <p>
      <strong>The Cerf Report</strong> is an independent publication and podcast focused on clear,
      evidence-driven analysis across technology, economics, geopolitics, and AI.
      The goal is to cut through narrative noise and explain the structural forces shaping
      markets and power.
    </p>
    
    <h2>Follow & Listen</h2>
    <p class="links">
      <a href="https://thecerfreport.substack.com/">Substack</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/TheCerfReport">X</a>
      <a href="https://bsky.app/profile/thecerfreport.bsky.social">Bluesky</a>
      <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/the-cerf-report/id1837946735">Apple Podcasts</a>
      <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/0fZLvBdnAtQrzPmSao0hBY">Spotify</a>
    </p>
    
    <h2>Editorial Focus</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>AI infrastructure and the compute economy</li>
      <li>Trade, tariffs, and industrial policy</li>
      <li>Technology platform power and market structure</li>
      <li>Second-order effects in geopolitics and markets</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Contact</h2>
